{"id":278587,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/02/维权网-杭州百名上访维权人士在市政府请愿被驱/","date":"2013-02-09T12:16:05Z","modified":"2013-02-09T12:16:05Z","title":"维权网 | 杭州百名上访维权人士在市政府请愿被驱赶（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员钱江报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>日</span><span>，杭州众多的拆迁受害人及其他蒙冤者们，因无法过年到市政府请愿，希望市委书记黄坤明和市长邵占维出来见见他们，关心一下他们，让他们安心过个年。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>上午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>点至</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>点半，近百名上访维权人士陆续到市政府前，望眼欲穿地等着黄书记、邵市长来看他们。大家认为，黄书记和邵市场心里惦着不会全是那些大老板，他们心里肯定也装着这些无家可归的贫困者，因为他们在官媒上的讲话很让老百姓感动的。但是大家没有想到，今天他们一到市政府门口，就从里出来很多人，其中有江干区信访局局长张泽民、副局长王卫达，有些人访民们从未见到过，还有很多警察。上访维权人士的诉求是“我们要家园，要饭吃”，但还没有等他们喊，这些市政府的官员们就大发雷霆，警察和保安强行将上访维权人士们驱离市政府门口。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>一些上访维权人士说，这种情况以前很少发生，大家本以为十八大之后，政府会关注民生，能解决上访维权者们的合理诉求，没想到请愿被驱赶，这使大家对十八大后抱有的一点点希望象肥皀泡一样地破灭，重新陷入无助和绝望之中。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-4zUMJ4DGz4U/URYQMNulWnI/AAAAAAAAck4/RbRCGIqXMsQ/s1600/IMG0208100301.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"227\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-4zUMJ4DGz4U/URYQMNulWnI/AAAAAAAAck4/RbRCGIqXMsQ/s320/IMG0208100301.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-jTgvZdHgWkw/URYQM2mC_XI/AAAAAAAAclA/oks4AWATItg/s1600/IMG0208114700.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-jTgvZdHgWkw/URYQM2mC_XI/AAAAAAAAclA/oks4AWATItg/s320/IMG0208114700.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-lVVyNZI3Cy0/URYQNgcBoaI/AAAAAAAAclI/-KQQGq6N0bA/s1600/JDJJT80O%60Y_Q%25_O0EMHBIT8.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"180\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-lVVyNZI3Cy0/URYQNgcBoaI/AAAAAAAAclI/-KQQGq6N0bA/s320/JDJJT80O%60Y_Q%25_O0EMHBIT8.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-3vtdRUuLru8/URYQRtecq4I/AAAAAAAAclQ/xMy4J6WdIIM/s1600/@3WNVNO%7B6%5D%5D$G1%5DE@BEI9G0.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"210\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-3vtdRUuLru8/URYQRtecq4I/AAAAAAAAclQ/xMy4J6WdIIM/s320/@3WNVNO%7B6%5D%5D$G1%5DE@BEI9G0.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[16910,19196]}